  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de GNOME Backgrounds</title>
    <para>
      Install <application>GNOME Backgrounds</application> by running the
      following  
    </para>
<screen>
<userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput>
</screen>
    <para>
      This package does not come with a test suite.
    </para>
    <para>
      Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> :
    </para>
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install</userinput>
</screen>
  </sect2>
